Do NOT expect anonymity when using Qubes start menu -> DisposableVM -> Firefox. It's better not to use that default Qubes start menu entry at all. This is because using any browser other than Tor Browser is discouraged if anonymity is desired. For reasoning, see [[Tor Browser]].
